verse = \lyricmode {
  My heart was sad as for a friend;
I mourned, my man -- tle I would rend
as one who sor -- rows for a bro -- ther
and who with grief la -- ments his mo -- ther.
But when I stum -- bled, they re -- joiced;
gath͜e͜r -- ing a -- round, their hate they voiced,
and wretch -- es whom I did not know
mocked me and glo -- ried in my woe.
}
